name: Norman Reedus
summary: Norman Reedus. Actor: The Walking Dead. Norman Reedus was born in Hollywood, Florida. He is of Italian, English, Scottish and Irish descent. He is an accomplished photographer with several books of his photography published and continues to do art shows in galleries all around the world every year.
